text:
1. Put on the skijet gear
2. Stand on the skijet
3. Start the skijet engine
4. Accelerate on the water
5. Maintain balance on the skijet
6. Navigate and steer the skijet
7. Control the speed of the skijet
8. Perform tricks or maneuvers (optional)
9. Slow down and stop the skijet
10. Disembark from the skijet
